hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I saw your advert in the paper con cret creatine pills MLB used every means at its disposal to bring the players it believed were using PEDs to justice, filing what was considered to be a longshot lawsuit against Bosch and others involved in Biogenesis, and purchasing damaging Biogenesis documents from Bosch's associates. Without subpoena power, MLB faced an uphill battle in convincing witnesses to cooperate -- but once the lawsuit was filed, and the defendants' lawyers' fees began to pile up, the wall of silence crumbled.
